###
### Embabel MCP Meeting Planner – REST examples
### Project: 04-embabel-mcp-meeting-planner (planner-agent module)
### Embabel: 0.4.0-SNAPSHOT | Spring Boot 3.5.13 | Java 21
### Mode: Spring Boot REST (programmatic invocation via AgentPlatform)
###
### Prerequisites:
###   1. Export OPENAI_API_KEY
###   2. Build location-mcp:
###      cd demos/04-embabel-mcp-meeting-planner/location-mcp && mvn package -DskipTests
###   3. Start planner-agent:
###      cd demos/04-embabel-mcp-meeting-planner/planner-agent && mvn spring-boot:run
###      (The agent starts the MCP server as a subprocess via stdio)
###
### Demo walkthrough order:
###   1. Flow A — Basel team meeting (find → check → book)
###   2. Flow B — Zürich client meeting with video (find → check → book)
###   3. Flow C — Large meeting in Bern (may need replanning if no room fits)
###

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api/meetings
@meetingEndpoint = {{baseUrl}}/plan

### ─── Flow A: Basel Team Meeting ────────────────────────────────────────
### Small team sync in Basel. 6 people, no video needed.
### Expected: Finds Basel HQ → selects an available room → books it
###
### Agent plan: RoomRequest → findLocation (MCP: all-locations) → Location
###           → findRoomAtLocation (MCP: check-room-availability) → SuggestedRoom
###           → bookRoom (MCP: book-room) → BookingResult
###
POST {{meetingEndpoint}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "meetingDescription": "Weekly team sync to review sprint progress",
  "numberOfPeople": 6,
  "preferredCity": "Basel",
  "date": "2026-04-22",
  "time": "10:00",
  "durationMinutes": 60,
  "needsVideoConference": false
}

### ─── Flow B: Zürich Client Meeting ─────────────────────────────────────
### Client presentation in Zürich. 4 people, video conference required.
### Expected: Finds Zürich Office → selects an available video-capable room → books it
###
POST {{meetingEndpoint}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "meetingDescription": "Quarterly business review with key client, needs presentation setup",
  "numberOfPeople": 4,
  "preferredCity": "Zürich",
  "date": "2026-04-23",
  "time": "14:00",
  "durationMinutes": 90,
  "needsVideoConference": true
}

### ─── Flow C: Large Bern Workshop ───────────────────────────────────────
### Workshop in Bern for 15 people. Bern hub only has 1 room (cap 10).
### Expected: May find Bern Hub but room too small → agent should handle gracefully
###           or select alternative location
###
POST {{meetingEndpoint}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "meetingDescription": "Cross-team architecture workshop, needs whiteboard and breakout space",
  "numberOfPeople": 15,
  "preferredCity": "Bern",
  "date": "2026-04-24",
  "time": "09:00",
  "durationMinutes": 180,
  "needsVideoConference": true
}
